Indonesian farmers will start cutting again. Madagascar cloves Dollars 770
cif, Dollars 850 spot; Zanzibar cloves spot Dollars 900. Mexico pimento
unchanged at Dollars 1,700 spot, shipment Dollars 1,650. Jamaica spot easier
at Dollars 2,175, shipment Dollars 2,140 and Guatemalan spot Dollars 1,900.
