FT  26 MAR 93 / Power price cut
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
EAST MIDLANDS Electricity is to cut electricity prices by an average 3.2 per
cent from April 1. It said the changes would result in savings of more than
Pounds 9 a year for the average domestic customer.
